import { Box, Center, Button, Grid, Image, Text, GridItem} from "@chakra-ui/react"

function NavBar() {
    return(
        <Box w="100%" h="150px" bgGradient="linear(to-t, blue.200, blue.900)" >
            <Grid w="">
                <Text
                bgGradient="linear(to-l, #7928CA,#FF0080)"
                bgClip="text"
                fontSize="6xl"
                fontWeight="semibold"
                >
                    Logo
                </Text>
            </Grid>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default NavBar;
